WEBVTT

00:01:27.536 --> 00:01:30.211
Rekel sem: "Solomon, če bova to počela,
greva na veliko.

00:01:30.235 --> 00:01:37.137
(aplavz)

00:01:38.286 --> 00:01:42.191
Zmorem to. Koliko zlata imaš?"

00:01:42.215 --> 00:01:45.302
(smeh)

00:01:45.681 --> 00:01:47.685
Rekel je: "Ni pomembno, koliko zlata imam,

00:01:47.685 --> 00:01:49.780
pomembna je tvoja
sposobnost ravnanja z njim.

00:01:49.780 --> 00:01:52.683
Lahko začnemo s poskusno pošiljko 50 kg.

00:01:52.707 --> 00:01:54.578
Rekel sem: "50 kg?

00:01:54.602 --> 00:01:56.245
Sploh nima smisla to početi,

00:01:56.269 --> 00:01:58.499
če ne pošlješ vsaj metrično tono."

00:01:58.523 --> 00:01:59.718
(smeh)

00:01:59.742 --> 00:02:02.511
(aplavz)